--Made by Luckymaxer --Updated for R15 avatars by StarWars
Tool = script.Parent Handle = Tool:WaitForChild("Handle") Mesh = Handle:WaitForChild("Mesh")
Players = game:GetService("Players") InsertService = game:GetService("InsertService")
Remover = script:WaitForChild("Remover")
FakeHandle = Tool:FindFirstChild("FakeHandle") if FakeHandle then FakeHandle:Destroy() Handle.Transparency = 0 end
ChopperModel = InsertService:LoadAsset(178339458) Chopper = ChopperModel:GetChildren()[1]:Clone() if ChopperModel and ChopperModel.Parent then ChopperModel:Destroy() end
MaxDistance = 10
ClientControl = (Tool:FindFirstChild("ClientControl") or Instance.new("RemoteFunction")) ClientControl.Name = "ClientControl" ClientControl.Parent = Tool
ServerControl = (Tool:FindFirstChild("ServerControl") or Instance.new("RemoteFunction")) ServerControl.Name = "ServerControl" ServerControl.Parent = Tool
DisplayModel = Tool:FindFirstChild("DisplayModel") if DisplayModel then DisplayModel:Destroy() end
Handle.Transparency = 0 Tool.Enabled = true
ClientControl.OnServerInvoke = (function(player, Mode, Value) if Mode == "Click" and Player == player then if Value and (not PlayerChopper or not PlayerChopper.Parent) then Handle.Transparency = 1 MakeChopper() end end end)
function MakeChopper() if PlayerChopper and PlayerChopper.Parent then PlayerChopper:Destroy() end PlayerChopper = Chopper:Clone() ChopperTorso = PlayerChopper:FindFirstChild("Torso") PlayerChopper:FindFirstChild("Creator").Value = Player local RemoverClone = Remover:Clone() RemoverClone.Disabled = false RemoverClone.Parent = PlayerChopper PlayerChopper.Parent = game:GetService("Workspace") ChopperTorso.CFrame = Torso.CFrame - Torso.CFrame.lookVector * ((ChopperTorso.Size.Z / 2) + (Torso.Size.Z / 2) + 5) ChopperTorso.CFrame = ChopperTorso.CFrame - Vector3.new(0, (Torso.Size.Y / 2), 0) end
function Equipped() Character = Tool.Parent Player = Players:GetPlayerFromCharacter(Character) Humanoid = Character:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") Torso = Character:FindFirstChild("Torso") or Character:FindFirstChild("UpperTorso") Handle.Transparency = 0 if not Player or not Humanoid or Humanoid.Health == 0 or not Torso then return end end
function Unequipped() for i, v in pairs({PlayerChopper}) do if v and v.Parent then v:Destroy() end end Handle.Transparency = 0 end
Tool.Equipped:connect(Equipped) Tool.Unequipped:connect(Unequipped)

--Made by Luckymaxer
Figure = script.Parent Creator = Figure:WaitForChild("Creator").Value
Debris = game:GetService("Debris")
function DestroyModel() Debris:AddItem(Figure, 2) end
if Creator:IsA("Player") then Character = Creator.Character if Character then Character.Changed:connect(function(Property) if not Character.Parent then DestroyModel() end end) else DestroyModel() end else DestroyModel() end

--Made by Luckymaxer
Tool = script.Parent Handle = Tool:WaitForChild("Handle")
Players = game:GetService("Players")
ClientControl = Tool:WaitForChild("ClientControl") ServerControl = Tool:WaitForChild("ServerControl")
function Click(Down) if not Player or not Humanoid or Humanoid.Health == 0 then return end pcall(function() ClientControl:InvokeServer("Click", Down) end) end
function Equipped(Mouse) Character = Tool.Parent Player = Players:GetPlayerFromCharacter(Character) Humanoid = Character:FindFirstChild("Humanoid") if not Player or not Humanoid or Humanoid.Health == 0 then return end Mouse.Button1Down:connect(function() Click(true) end) end
function Unequipped() end
Tool.Equipped:connect(Equipped) Tool.Unequipped:connect(Unequipped)

--Made by Luckymaxer
Mouse_Icon = "rbxasset://textures/GunCursor.png" Reloading_Icon = "rbxasset://textures/GunWaitCursor.png"
Tool = script.Parent
Mouse = nil
function UpdateIcon() if Mouse then Mouse.Icon = Tool.Enabled and Mouse_Icon or Reloading_Icon end end
function OnEquipped(ToolMouse) Mouse = ToolMouse UpdateIcon() end
function OnChanged(Property) if Property == "Enabled" then UpdateIcon() end end
Tool.Equipped:connect(OnEquipped) Tool.Changed:connect(OnChanged)
